    • playerAdded

      public void playerAdded​(org.json.simple.JSONObject file)
      once the server accepts "PlayerValues" it sends out a JSONObject with id, name and figure to all Clients. This function sets your own name and figure(if you were the client who sent the "PlayerValues" Object), and if it was someone else this function just sets playerName*Robot*, playerID*Robot* and available*Robot* in every dataModel.

      file - msgBody of the JSONObject
